## 10. Future Requirements

### 10.1 Backend Integration (Phase 2)

#### FR-BE-001: Server-Side Form Processing
**Priority:** HIGH  
**Description:** Process contact form submissions server-side.

**Requirements:**
- RESTful API endpoint for form submission
- Database storage (PostgreSQL/MySQL)
- Email notification system
- Admin dashboard for viewing submissions

**Technologies:**
- Node.js + Express, OR
- Python + Django/Flask, OR
- PHP + Laravel

#### FR-BE-002: Content Management System
**Priority:** MEDIUM  
**Description:** Admin interface for managing vegetables and regions.

**Requirements:**
- CRUD operations for vegetables
- CRUD operations for regions
- Image upload capability
- Bulk import/export (CSV)

#### FR-BE-003: User Authentication
**Priority:** MEDIUM  
**Description:** User accounts for farmers and buyers.

**Requirements:**
- Registration system
- Login/logout
- Password reset
- Role-based access control (RBAC)
- OAuth integration (Google, Facebook)

### 10.2 Advanced Features (Phase 3)

#### FR-ADV-001: Real-Time Pricing
**Priority:** HIGH  
**Description:** Dynamic pricing based on market conditions.

**Requirements:**
- API integration with commodity markets
- Real-time price updates
- Historical price charts
- Price alerts for users

#### FR-ADV-002: Inventory Management
**Priority:** HIGH  
**Description:** Track available inventory from farmers.

**Requirements:**
- Farmer dashboard for listing products
- Stock quantity tracking
- Expiration date management
- Quality grading system

#### FR-ADV-003: Order Management
**Priority:** HIGH  
**Description:** End-to-end order processing system.

**Requirements:**
- Shopping cart functionality
- Checkout process
- Payment gateway integration (Stripe, Razorpay)
- Order tracking
- Invoice generation

#### FR-ADV-004: Logistics Integration
**Priority:** MEDIUM  
**Description:** Track shipments and deliveries.

**Requirements:**
- Integration with shipping APIs
- Real-time tracking
- Delivery scheduling
- Cold chain monitoring (IoT sensors)

### 10.3 AI/ML Features (Phase 4)

#### FR-AI-001: Price Prediction
**Priority:** MEDIUM  
**Description:** ML model to predict future prices.

**Requirements:**
- Historical price data analysis
- Seasonal pattern recognition
- Market trend forecasting
- 90% prediction accuracy (within Â±10%)

**Technologies:**
- Python + scikit-learn
- TensorFlow/PyTorch
- Time series analysis (ARIMA, LSTM)

#### FR-AI-002: Quality Assessment
**Priority:** MEDIUM  
**Description:** Image recognition for quality grading.

**Requirements:**
- Upload product images
- Automated quality scoring (Grade A/B/C)
- Defect detection
- 85%+ accuracy rate

**Technologies:**
- Computer Vision (OpenCV)
- Deep Learning (CNN models)
- TensorFlow/PyTorch

#### FR-AI-003: Chatbot Assistant
**Priority:** LOW  
**Description:** AI chatbot for farmer queries.

**Requirements:**
- Natural language understanding
- Multi-language support (English, Hindi, regional)
- FAQs automation
- Human handoff for complex queries

**Technologies:**
- NLP (spaCy, NLTK)
- Dialogflow or Rasa
- GPT integration

### 10.4 Mobile Application (Phase 5)

#### FR-MOB-001: Native Mobile Apps
**Priority:** MEDIUM  
**Description:** iOS and Android applications.

**Requirements:**
- Feature parity with web version
- Offline mode support
- Push notifications
- Camera integration for product photos
- GPS for farmer location

**Technologies:**
- React Native, OR
- Flutter, OR
- Native (Swift for iOS, Kotlin for Android)

#### FR-MOB-002: Progressive Web App (PWA)
**Priority:** HIGH  
**Description:** Convert website to PWA.

**Requirements:**
- Service worker for offline caching
- Add to home screen functionality
- Push notifications
- Fast load times (App-like experience)

**Technologies:**
- Service Workers
- Web App Manifest
- IndexedDB for offline storage

### 10.5 Internationalization (Phase 6)

#### FR-I18N-001: Multi-Language Support
**Priority:** MEDIUM  
**Description:** Support for Indian regional languages.

**Languages:**
- English (default)
- Hindi
- Tamil
- Telugu
- Marathi
- Gujarati
- Bengali

**Requirements:**
- Language switcher in header
- RTL support (if needed)
- Localized content for vegetables/regions
- Date/number formatting per locale

#### FR-I18N-002: Currency Conversion
**Priority:** MEDIUM  
**Description:** Support for multiple currencies.

**Currencies:**
- USD (default)
- INR
- EUR
- GBP
- AED

**Requirements:**
- Real-time exchange rates API
- Automatic conversion based on user location
- Manual currency selection option

### 10.6 Analytics and Reporting (Phase 7)

#### FR-ANA-001: Web Analytics
**Priority:** HIGH  
**Description:** Track user behavior and engagement.

**Metrics:**
- Page views
- User sessions
- Bounce rate
- Conversion rate (form submissions)
- Popular vegetables/regions

**Tools:**
- Google Analytics 4
- Mixpanel
- Custom analytics dashboard

#### FR-ANA-002: Business Intelligence
**Priority:** MEDIUM  
**Description:** Advanced reporting for business insights.

**Requirements:**
- Sales reports
- Farmer performance metrics
- Regional demand analysis
- Seasonal trends
- Export destination reports

**Tools:**
- Tableau
- Power BI
- Custom dashboard with Chart.js/D3.js

