## Appendix B: Testing Requirements

### Unit Testing
- Form validation functions
- Utility functions (if any)
- Data formatting functions

### Integration Testing
- Navigation flow
- Form submission process
- Responsive behavior across breakpoints

### User Acceptance Testing (UAT)
